OL,3,CMan charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged assault in Ebbw Vale
OL,6,FA 30-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith manslaughter after a man died
OL,8,Ffollowing an assault in Ebbw Vale.
OL,10,FThe man, from Cardiff, was remanded in
OL,11,Fcustody and is due to appear before
OL,12,FNewport Magistrates' Court on Thursday
OL,13,F26 February.
OL,15,FGwent Police officers were called to
OL,16,FThe Picture House in Bethcar Street,
OL,17,FEbbw Vale, following reports of an
OL,18,Fassault outside the pub between
OL,19,F11.30pm on Friday 20 February and
OL,20,F12.15am on Saturday 21 February.
