OL,3,CMan charged with manslaughter
OL,4,Cfollowing alleged assault in Ebbw Vale
OL,6,FMarcus Lee Carpenter a 37-year-old,
OL,7,Ffrom Tredegar, had been in a life-
OL,8,Fthreatening condition in hospital; he
OL,9,Flater died from his injuries.
OL,11,FHis family has been informed and are
OL,12,Freceiving support from specialist
OL,13,Fofficers.
OL,15,FEnquiries are ongoing and anyone with
OL,16,Fany information is asked to call
OL,17,Fpolice on 101, quoting 2600055384.
OL,18,FAlternatively, you can call
OL,19,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,20,F111 or visit their website.
